## ğŸ—ï¸ Architecture

### Core Systems

#### GameClock
- Manages game time (1 real second = 1 game hour)
- Emits events for hourly, daily, monthly, and yearly updates
- Handles pause/resume and speed controls

#### City
- Economic class distribution (6 classes)
- Demographics calculation (working age, employed, unemployed)
- Purchasing power computation
- Infrastructure tracking (airport, seaport, railway)

#### CityManager
- Manages all cities in the simulation
- Handles city generation and updates
- Calculates distances and shipping costs

#### TransportationNetwork
- 5 transport types with realistic costs
- Distance-based cost calculation
- Infrastructure requirements
- Transit time computation

#### SimulationEngine
- Coordinates all systems
- Processes hourly, daily, monthly, yearly updates
- Manages corporations and products
- Tracks market history and events

### UI Components

#### Dashboard
- Updates all interface elements
- Handles user interactions
- Manages control buttons
- Populates data displays

#### MapRenderer
- Renders interactive city map
- Handles city selection
- Draws transportation routes
- Updates in real-time

